          towards the South China Sea. Puri Tri Agung, situated on the eastern
          route of Bangka, is approximately 20 kilometers from Pangkal Pinang
          City. The building is round in shape and almost 30 meters high. The
          spacious courtyard allows visitors to enjoy the beautiful scenery
        </p>

        <p class="text-home">
