          Buddha statues, and even the open sea. Since its opening in 2015,
          visitors to Puri Tri Agung have come from various parts of the
          country. The magnificence of Puri Tri Agung and the beauty of the
          surrounding nature can be enjoyed for free.
        </p>

        <p class="text-home">
          Puri Tri Agung symbolizes the three teachings of Tri Dharma,
          consisting of Confucianism, Buddhism, and Taoism. Followers of
          Confucian teachings can not only visit but also perform worship there.
          Visitors can also learn about Confucian teachings and history through
          notes and photos displayed on the walls of the puri. Currently, Puri
          Tri Agung has become one of the iconic tourist destinations in the
          region. So, what are you waiting for? Visit Puri Tri Agung and enjoy
